%F A337004 Morphism 1 -> 1,1,-1,-1,1 and -1 -> 1,1,-1,-1,-1 starting from 1.
%F A337004 G.f.: Sum_{k>=0} (x^(5^k) + x^(2*5^k) - x^(3*5^k) - x^(4*5^k)) / (1 - x^(5^(k+1))).
